metadata.name: Two-Spirit Prairie Sky #1/4
metadata.description:
It came to me during a nap. I thought about a relative, a Queer Métis person, looking up to the vast prairie sky. They are wrapped in a Métis-reminiscent shawl, sewn with love and medicine, by their loving chosen family. The sky reflects back an ancestor, a massive sweeping cloud, swirling. An eagle, a conduit of love, appears amongst the swirl.

Date: 06-06-2022 

Platform: Midjourney, Photoshop  
Prompt: ​​A_person_with_two_spirits_Metis_sash_flying_floatin
